    "title": "Grad School pt. 1",
    "description": "Everything before this drawing was before entering my PhD program. Everything after this drawing was after entering PhD. \n\n&quot;It&quot; is a lightbulb because Universe is made of thought. \n\n&quot;It&quot; has holes because while an incandescent filament requires a vacuum to burn, Life is in constant reciprocal interplay with the ecosystem. \n\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\n\n&quot;Last Sunday morning, the sunshine felt like rain.\nThe week before, they all seemed the same.\nWith the help of God and true friends, I've come to realize,\nI still have two strong legs, and even wings to fly.&quot;\n              -Allman Brothers\n\n",
